Title: TypeScript just overtook Python and JavaScript
Author: GitHub
Description:
In a historic shift, TypeScript has overtaken Python and JavaScript to become the top language on GitHub in the 2025 Octoverse report. Idan Gazit shares his thoughts on why this happened, citing the language's versatility across devices, and predicts how WebAssembly might shake things up in the future.
